    </div>
    <div class="trust-sep"></div>
    <div class="trust-item rv rv-d2">
      <div class="trust-num">99.97%</div>
      <div class="trust-label">Uptime</div>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-sep"></div>
    <div class="trust-badges rv rv-d3">
      <div class="trust-badge">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
        256-bit encrypted
      </div>
      <div class="trust-badge">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
        SOC 2 compliant
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<%# Features %>
<section class="section" id="features" data-controller="landing--reveal">
  <div class="section-label rv">Capabilities</div>
  <div class="section-title rv rv-d1">Three tools.<br>One workflow.</div>
  <div class="section-desc rv rv-d2">Each works independently. Together they cover the full loop from data to decision to action.</div>

  <div class="feat-grid stagger">
    <div class="feat-card rv">
      <div class="feat-tag blue">Real-time data</div>
      <h3>Live price feed for 8,400+ assets</h3>
      <p>Alpaca and Finnhub WebSockets deliver sub-second updates. Stocks, crypto, forex — unified in one stream. Search any publicly traded asset without signing up.</p>
      <div class="feat-data">
        <span style="color:var(--text-muted)">AAPL</span> <span>258.90</span> <span style="color:var(--gain)">+2.13%</span><br>
        <span style="color:var(--text-muted)">BTC</span>&nbsp; <span>71,242</span> <span style="color:var(--gain)">+3.71%</span><br>
        <span style="color:var(--text-muted)">TSLA</span> <span>341.98</span> <span style="color:var(--loss)">-1.35%</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="feat-card rv">
      <div class="feat-tag green">Alerts</div>
      <h3>Condition-based notifications</h3>
      <p>Price targets, RSI/MACD crossovers, volume spikes, news sentiment. Delivered via Telegram, email, or WhatsApp within seconds.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat-card rv">
      <div class="feat-tag purple">AI Analysis</div>
      <h3>Daily market briefs</h3>
      <p>Gemini 2.5 Flash scans your watchlist every morning. Plain-English insights on technicals, news, and earnings — not chart screenshots.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<%# How It Works %>
<section class="section" id="how" data-controller="landing--reveal">
  <div style="text-align:center">
    <div class="section-label rv">Setup</div>
    <div class="section-title rv rv-d1">Four steps. Under a minute.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step rv"><div class="step-line"></div><div class="step-num">1</div><h4>Sign up</h4><p>Email + password. No card.</p></div>
    <div class="step rv rv-d1"><div class="step-line"></div><div class="step-num">2</div><h4>Add assets</h4><p>Search 8,400+ stocks, crypto, forex.</p></div>
    <div class="step rv rv-d2"><div class="step-line"></div><div class="step-num">3</div><h4>Set conditions</h4><p>Price, technicals, or volume.</p></div>
    <div class="step rv rv-d3"><div class="step-num">4</div><h4>Get alerts</h4><p>Telegram, email, or WhatsApp.</p></div>
  </div>
</section>

